Open the bottom drawer of the tall white dresser and put the bottle of lotion inside all the way to the right.
Turn left and take a step forward, then turn left again and walk up to the white table.
Pick up the bottle of lotion off of the table.
Turn left and take a step forward, then turn left again and walk up to the tall white dresser.
Open the bottom drawer of the dresser and put the bottle of lotion inside to the left of the bottle that's already in there.
